  m_text: "<style=title>Magic</style>\n<b>Head Throw</b>\nDullahan throws their head
    to the enemy, killing them if they aren't a boss, otherwise, they\u2019ll deal
    POWx2 damages. If Dullahan has a [{item_needed}] in their Inventory, the cost
    of this spell is the item instead."
